<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6015472">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6015472/" class="title-link">不同风格的语言！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6015472"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/66925399/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u66925399-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/66925399/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小楽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-06-09"
      class="main-meta">2013-06-09 10:39:23</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6015472_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  买这本书是 在上海季风书园买的。那天刚好经过季风书园上海图书馆店的时候，看到有金老师的签售会，以前没有怎么读过他的作品，但在网上了解过他。那天签售会金老师与读者共同讨论了中国以前的宪政和未来的宪政，讨论非常激烈，感觉几小时受益匪浅。  这本书是金老师的最新力作...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6015472_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6015472_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










